Class name: OrderManager
Parent class: None
Interface: Manager

Responsibilities:
* Manage orders stored in OrderStorage.
* When we call methods in OrderManager, we can do the following:
    - search (return the order with specific id)
    - findBuyer (return all orders made from a certain buyer)
    - addElement (add order(s) to OrderStorage)
    - removeElement (when user wants to delete the order information, we can offer this option
                     and delete the order form the OrderStorage))

Collaborators:
- OrderStorage
- Manager(interface)